Package: craibm
Title: Individual-Based Model for Sportfish Population Simulation
Version: 0.2.9
Authors@R: person("Developer", "Name", email = "dev@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shiny application for parameterizing and running individual-based
    models for sportfish populations with parallel batch simulation.
